Interface EntityLoadQueryBuilder

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    EntityLoadQueryBuilderImpl

    public interface EntityLoadQueryBuilder
    Contract for generating the query (currently the SQL string specifically) based on a LoadPlan with a single root EntityReturn
